Bug name: 
Elwyyn Forest Quest... Further Concerns
######################
Bug Priority: 
Low Priority
######################
Bug Type: 
Questing
######################
Bug Description:
When accepting the quest [Further Concerns], you do not have the option to "ride a steed" to the location. Quest ID:"http://www.wowhead.com/quest=35/further-concerns"
The quest description can be quoted from wowhead.com... "I have here a Stormwind charger that will take you to Guard Thomas. Let me know if you wish to make use of the horse."
